About the American Optometric Association American Eye-Q survey:
The tenth annual AOA American Eye-Q" survey was created and commissioned in conjunction with Penn,
Schoen & Berland Associates (PSB). From February 19 - -March 4, 2015, PSB conducted 1,000 online interviews
among Americans 18 years and older who embodied a nationally representative sample of the U.S. general
population. (Margin of error is plus or minus 3.10 percentage points at a 95% confidence level.)
